
    Use `python3` for these scripts.

    Usage:
    ```
        # pwd = BusinessLogic

        # Venv
            python3 -m venv venv
            source venv/bin/activate
            pip3 install -r requirements.txt
            pip3 install -U pip google-api-python-client

        # Run script
            python3 measure_performance.py \
                --bundle_id TODO \
                --app_name TODO \
                --app_path TODO \
                --repo_github_token TODO \
                --repo_owner TODO \
                --repo_name TODO \
                --pr_number TODO
    ```
